Filter::NumberLines - Source filter for Numbering lines.
========================================================

SYNOPSIS
========
    Just put use Filter::NumberLines; at the top of your source file (below
    the shebang). It will automagically number your lines starting from the
    line after the use statement.

      use Filter::NumberLines;

NOTE
    This module is used in the Source Filters in Perl talk I gave at
    YAPC::Eu 2.00.2 in Munich.

REQUIREMENTS
    Filter::NumberLines requires Filter::Util::Call.
    Filter::NumberLines::Simple requires Filter::Simple.
    Filter::NumberLines::Scratch requires nothing.

